'''李察·阿倫·尼萊'''（{{lang-en|'''Richard Alan Naylor'''}}，{{bd|1977年|2月28日|catIdx=Naylor, Richard}}），簡稱'''李察·尼萊'''（{{lang-en|'''Richard Naylor'''}}），出生在[[列斯|列斯]]，是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]職業足球員，司職[[中堅|中堅]]，現效力[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]。

==生平==
;葉士域治
尼萊出身自[[葉士域治足球會|葉士域治]]的青訓系統並效力了14年之久。他在1990年代中期時是以[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]身份上陣，然而具備潛質的他在經歷了數次傷患後，開始發現自己被{{Link-en|亞歷斯·默菲|Alex Mathie}}、{{Link-en|占士·史葛哥洛夫|James Scowcroft}}、{{Link-en|大衛·莊臣|David Johnson (footballer born 1976)}}和後來的{{Link-en|馬庫斯·史超活|Marcus Stewart}}所超越，成為[[樸文路球場|樸文路球場]]的第五前鋒。

1999/00年球季，尼萊雖然在開季時表現不俗，但又再一次被迫坐板凳，卻又在對[[班士利足球會|班士利]]的附加賽決賽中發揮關鍵作用<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2000-06-29
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/776924.stm
|title=Play-off joy at last for Burley's Ipswich
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2020-09-03
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903105338/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/776924.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。他在上半場時入替受傷的大衛·莊臣後攻入一球，協助葉士域治自1995年以來首次升上[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英超]]。

當葉士域治升上英超後，尼萊再次被時任領隊{{Link-en|佐治·貝利|George Burley}}投閒置散。2000/01年球季，葉士域治取得了[[歐洲足協盃|歐協盃]]資格，而尼萊亦零星地代表球會上陣並在對[[打比郡足球會|打比郡]]的賽事中攻入葉士域治在當季的最後一球<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2001-05-19
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/1338654.stm
|title=Derby dent Ipswich hopes
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-01-13
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113025328/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/1338654.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

2001/02年球季，尼萊並不在葉士域治的計劃之中，儘管他有機會在歐協盃對[[意大利|意大利]]球會[[國際米蘭足球會|國際米蘭]]的賽事中上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2001-12-06
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/uefa_cup/1693221.stm
|title=Vieri stuns Ipswich
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2012-01-24
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124072803/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/uefa_cup/1693221.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，不過他仍然在2002年被球會先後外借至[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2002-03-04
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/1854354.stm
|title=Naylor joins Barnsley
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307152220/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/barnsley/1854354.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>和[[米禾爾足球會|米禾爾]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2002-01-29
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1788733.stm
|title=Lions snap up Naylor
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307021620/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/millwall/1788733.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

葉士域治在2001/02年球季降班後，{{Link-en|祖·萊爾|Joe Royle}}成為新任領隊，隨著大量球員在降班後離去，尼萊得以被重用。祖·萊爾決定讓他轉為出任中堅。

2003/04年球季，尼萊在推動葉士域治升班方面發揮了關鍵作用。2004/05年球季，葉士域治打進了附加賽卻敗給[[韋斯咸足球會|韋斯咸]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2004-05-18
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3713951.stm
|title=West Ham reach final
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2004-05-22
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040522142811/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3713951.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，不過在2005/06年球季，球會卻不甚成功。2006年，祖·萊爾離開了葉士域治並由尼萊的前隊友{{Link-en|占·馬捷頓|Jim Magilton}}接任領隊一職。2005年10月1日，他由於效力葉士域治達10年而安排舉行紀念賽<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2005-10-01
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/4312008.stm
|title=Naylor handed Ipswich testimonial
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307025711/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/4312008.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。2006年9月3日，在葉士域治對溫布萊2000XI的賽事中，他在最後一分鐘射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]，協助球隊以3-3戰平對手<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2006-09-03
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/5310144.stm
|title=Naylor thanks fans for turn-out
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307082530/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/i/ipswich_town/5310144.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。2008/09年球季，尼萊接替原[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]{{Link-en|積臣·迪禾斯|Jason de Vos}}擔任球會隊長。

;列斯聯
2009年1月15日，尼萊被外借至[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2009-01-15
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7829358.stm
|title=Naylor completes Leeds loan deal
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307044124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7829358.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。2009年2月2日，他正式轉會至列斯聯<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2009-02-02
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7865916.stm
|title=Defender Naylor seals Leeds move
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307065329/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/7865916.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。他被任命為球隊的副隊長並在對[[修安聯足球會|修安聯]]的賽事中攻入其加盟以來的首球，協助球隊以2-0擊敗對手<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2009-01-27
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7847260.stm
|title=Leeds 2-0 Southend
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307150021/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7847260.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

2009年7月，尼萊接替了於[[夏天|夏天]]離開的[[費沙·李察臣|費沙·李察臣]]的[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]職務<ref>{{en}}[http://www.leedsunited.com/news/naylor-named-club-captain-20090731_2247585_1739665 NAYLOR NAMED CLUB CAPTAIN ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.leedsunited.com/news/naylor-named-club-captain-20090731_2247585_1739665 |date=20160303200747 }}</ref>。他接受了背部手術後缺陣了所有季前賽和一場[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|聯賽]]賽事<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2009-06-26
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8121003.stm
|title=Leeds skipper out for six weeks
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307055733/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8121003.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>，期間由[[莊拿芬·侯臣|莊拿芬·侯臣]]代任隊長<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2004-05-18
|url=http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Leeds-United-Jonny39s-pride-at.5608342.jp
|title=Leeds United: Jonny's pride at captaincy role
|publisher=約克郡晚報
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091006205801/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Leeds-United-Jonny39s-pride-at.5608342.jp
|archive-date=2009-10-06
|dead-url=yes
}}</ref>。9月17日，他在對[[米杜士堡足球會|米杜士堡]]的預備組賽事中於61分鐘後備入替復出<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
|date=2009-09-17
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8260243.stm
|title=Skipper Naylor makes Leeds return
|publisher=BBC
|accessdate=2009-10-02
|archive-date=2016-03-07
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307094859/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8260243.stm
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。9月29日，他復出後在[[艾蘭路球場|艾蘭路球場]]對[[卡素爾聯足球會|卡素爾]]的賽事中首次正選上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
