|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

2011年5月9日，尼萊獲領隊[[西蒙·加利臣|西蒙·加利臣]]通知於球季結束約滿後遭放棄<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13338686.stm |title=Club captain Richard Naylor to exit Leeds United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-09 |accessdate=2011-07-12 |archive-date=2011-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512002622/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13338686.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;唐卡士打及洛達咸
2011年7月11日尼萊以短約形式加盟[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/9535499.stm |title=Doncaster Rovers complete signing of Richard Naylor |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-11 |accessdate=2011-07-12 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/doncaster/9535499.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間上陣13場聯賽和2場聯賽盃賽事，於2012年1月約滿後離隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.eatsleepsport.com/doncaster-rovers/eagles-swoop-for-dumbuya-1363517.html#.TxEj-KVDt2A |title=Eagles swoop for Dumbuya |publisher=''eatsleepsport.com'' |date=2012-01-05 |accessdate=2012-01-14 }}{{Dead link}}</ref>。

